title: Spanish chicken traybake
ingredients: ['2 tins chickpeas, drained and rinsed', '2 large sweet red peppers, roughly chopped', '200g chorizo, chopped', '2 onions, roughly chopped', '7 small tomatoes, quartered', '9 cloves garlic, chopped', '1 teaspoon cumin seeds, crushed', '2 teaspoons smoked paprika', '1 teaspoon sea salt flakes', '3 tablespoons olive oil', '7 chicken thighs']
